description: This guy looked like a fool who had no idea how to dress for a job interview. To my surprise he turned out to be a rather eccentric robot enthusiast. He had some very valuable experience in servicing machines. The guy even dreamed of having his own robot company. Very interesting stuff, I was barely able to keep up. I thought he was a bit irresponsible and immature, maybe that's why he needed my help to find him a job. It took me only a few seconds to pick the right position for him. Unfortunately, our young scientist spent the weekend partying and was absolutely broke. I had the suspicion that he came to the interview straight from the party. He wasn't even wearing underwear... I couldn't let such a cutie to slip through my fingers. Thank god he was no nerd and definitely knew how to have fun!
title: Dirty Scout 239
